	(8, 'Saptari Hoedaja', 'Director', 'Saptari Hoedaja is an Indonesian citizen, born on May 30, 1959. He earned a Bachelor\'s degree from the Department of Mechanical Engineering, Bandung Institute of Technology (ITB) in 1983.Saptari Hoedaja began his career at Mitsubishi Motor Corporation, Japan in 1983. Later he worked as a Manager at Citibank NA, Jakarta from 1986 - 1989, as Vice President / Business Manager at PT Bank Bumiputera from 1989 - 1992, and as Vice President / Treasury & Financial Institute at PT Bank Universal from 1992 - 1993, and served as Senior General Manager / Treasury & Banking Relationship at PT Astra International from 1993 - 1995. Furthermore, from 1995 to 1997 he served as Managing Director of PT Astra Securities. In 1997, he was appointed as Commissioner at PT Bakrie Swasakti Utama until 1999. He also served as Director of PT Bakrie Land Development from 1997 to 2001. In 1997 he was appointed as Senior Vice President of PT Bakrie Capital Indonesia (Holding), until becoming CEO in 1998. Saptari Hoedaja\'s career continued as Director of PT Bakrie & Brothers Tbk in 2008 - 2010. Then in 2011, he was appointed as Chief Executive Officer of BUMI PLC until 2012. In 2007, he was appointed as President Commissioner of PT Energi Mega Persada Tbk. Since 2009, he served as Director of Bakrie Agro Commodity International PTE LTD, and Director of Bakrie AN International PTE LTD. In 2009 he was appointed as Commissioner of PT Petromine Energy Trading, and serving as President Director since 2010. Since 2011, he has been appointed as Director of Bakrie Petroleum International PTE LTD. He also serving as President Director of PT Arutmin Indonesia since 2011, and President Director of PT Kaltim Prima Coal since 2011. Since 2010, he was appointed as President Commissioner of PT Bumi Resources Minerals Tbk. He also serving as President Director of PT Bumi Resources Tbk since 2001 until now.', 'Directors', 'image_2020_10/saptari_hoedaja_01012932.jpg', '2020-10