	(11, 'business-ethics', '{"description_en":"<p><img style=\\"width: 790px;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/storage\\/summernote\\/summernote20201001121352.jpg\\"><\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company has established a reporting and complaint mechanism or comprehensive Whistle Blower System.<\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company has a whistleblowing procedure which regulates matters related to violation, including those that deal with integrity, such as bribery, corruption, the giving and receiving of gifts, and other activities which could potentially cause loss to the Company and damage the Company\\u2019s reputation.<\\/p><ul style=\\"outline: none; margin-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 15px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); font-family: Raleway, sans-serif;\\"><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To accelerate the achievement of vision, mission, goals, and targets determined by the Company.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To maximize the Company\\u2019s value by improving the implementation of transparency, independency, accountability, responsibility, and fairness principles in performing the Company\\u2019s activity.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To convince Shareholders that the Company is managed properly in order to provide reasonable and excellent results.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To realize the implementation of professional, transparent, and efficient corporate governance.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To create a culture of making decision based on high moral value and compliance with the prevailing laws and regulations within the environment of all organs of the Company.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To realize the implementation of corporate social responsibility to stakeholders.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To implement GCG principles so as to enhance the Company\\u2019s reputation and performance, as well as the Company\\u2019s value for the Shareholders.<\\/li><\\/ul>","description_id":"<p><img style=\\"width: 790px;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/storage\\/summernote\\/summernote20201001121352.jpg\\"><\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company has established a reporting and complaint mechanism or comprehensive Whistle Blower System.<\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company has a whistleblowing procedure which regulates matters related to violation, including those that deal with integrity, such as bribery, corruption, the giving and receiving of gifts, and other activities which could potentially cause loss to the Company and damage the Company\\u2019s reputation.<\\/p><ul style=\\"outline: none; margin-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 15px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); font-family: Raleway, sans-serif;\\"><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To accelerate the achievement of vision, mission, goals, and targets determined by the Company.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To maximize the Company\\u2019s value by improving the implementation of transparency, independency, accountability, responsibility, and fairness principles in performing the Company\\u2019s activity.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To convince Shareholders that the Company is managed properly in order to provide reasonable and excellent results.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To realize the implementation of professional, transparent, and efficient corporate governance.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To create a culture of making decision based on high moral value and compliance with the prevailing laws and regulations within the environment of all organs of the Company.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To realize the implementation of corporate social responsibility to stakeholders.<\\/li><li style=\\"outline: none; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">To implement GCG principles so as to enhance the Company\\u2019s reputation and performance, as well as the Company\\u2019s value for the Shareholders.<\\/li><\\/ul>"}', '2020-09-30 05:57:51', '2020-10-01 12:14:27'),
	(12, 'code-of-conduct', '{"description_en":"<p><img style=\\"width: 1440px;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/storage\\/summernote\\/summernote20201001121608.jpg\\"><\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company\\u2019s Reputation and Reliability are closely linked to the Company\\u2019s attitude when interacting with the stakeholders. Besides having to comply with the applicable laws and regulations, the Company must also pay attention to moral norms and etiquette so that the Company can enhance and strengthen the Company\\u2019s positive image. Therefore, the Company issues guidance that contains norms and ethics outlined in the Company\\u2019s Code of Conduct.<\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company has developed Code of Conduct in accordance with mission, vision, corporate values. The Code of Conduct serves as guidance for every individual in Darma Henwa to cooperate with internal and external parties. The Code of Conduct is introduced to all ranks in the Company and is included in work contract of employee recruitment, which must be understood and signed by all employees. Afterwards, all employees are expected to behave according to corporate values and to implement the Code of Conduct in daily activities.<\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/storage\\/document_2020_09\\/26030721.pdf\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Code Of Conduct<\\/a><br><\\/p>","description_id":"<p><img style=\\"width: 1440px;\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/storage\\/summernote\\/summernote20201001121608.jpg\\"><\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company\\u2019s Reputation and Reliability are closely linked to the Company\\u2019s attitude when interacting with the stakeholders. Besides having to comply with the applicable laws and regulations, the Company must also pay attention to moral norms and etiquette so that the Company can enhance and strengthen the Company\\u2019s positive image. Therefore, the Company issues guidance that contains norms and ethics outlined in the Company\\u2019s Code of Conduct.<\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">The Company has developed Code of Conduct in accordance with mission, vision, corporate values. The Code of Conduct serves as guidance for every individual in Darma Henwa to cooperate with internal and external parties. The Code of Conduct is introduced to all ranks in the Company and is included in work contract of employee recruitment, which must be understood and signed by all employees. Afterwards, all employees are expected to behave according to corporate values and to implement the Code of Conduct in daily activities.<\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\"><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/storage\\/document_2020_09\\/26030721.pdf\\" target=\\"_blank\\">Code Of Conduct<\\/a><br><\\/p>"}', '2020-09-30 05:57:59', '2020-10-01 12:17:58'),
