	(8, 'document_2020_09/26030721.pdf', '{"en":"Good Corporate Governance Committee Charter","id":"Good Corporate Governance Committee Charter"}', '{"en":"<p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">In order to encourage the Company\\u2019s management according to GCG principles and carry out Social and Environmental Responsibility as stated in Law No. 40 of 2007 concerning Limited Liability Company and Government Regulation No. 47 of 2012 concerning Social and Environmental Responsibility, the Board of Commissioners has established GCG Committee, which works collectively, professionally, and independently, in helping the Board of Commissioners in discharging its supervisory and advisory duties and functions, namely monitoring and ensuring the implementation of effective and sustainable good corporate governance in Darma Henwa.<\\/p><p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">GCG Committee Charter is drawn up as guideline for GCG Committee in implementing its duties and responsibilities according to the laws and regulations.<\\/p>","id":"<p style=\\"outline: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(130, 130, 130); line-height: 24px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\\">In order to encourage the Company\\u2019s management according to GCG principles and carry out Social and Environmental Responsibility as stated in Law No. 40 of 2007 concerning Limited Liability Company and Government Regulation No. 47 of 2012 concerning Social and Environmental Responsibility, the Board of Commissioners has established GCG Committee, which works collectively, professionally, and independently, in helping the Board of Commissioners in discharging its supervisory and advisory duties and functions, nam